    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "45131069_3_5104-5139",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "5104-5139",
      "markText": "在中东待过数十年的经验告诉他，个人承诺可能比一份精心起草的合同更重要。",
      "totalCount": 255,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=45131069&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5104&rangeEnd=5139",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c073221072b0a53dc07a5de?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5104&rangeEnd=5139"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "45131069_3_12613-12648",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "12613-12648",
      "markText": "他神秘地回答说，他没回复本身就应该被视为一种回复。然后他就挂断了电话。",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=45131069&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=12613&rangeEnd=12648",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c073221072b0a53dc07a5de?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=12613&rangeEnd=12648"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "45131069_3_16712-16792",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "16712-16792",
      "markText": "大宗商品交易商的基本业务简单至极：在一个地方和时间购买自然资源，然后在另一个地方和时间出售——希望能从中获利。它们之所以能发挥作用，是因为商品供求往往存在矛盾。",
      "totalCount": 216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=45131069&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=16712&rangeEnd=16792",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c073221072b0a53dc07a5de?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=16712&rangeEnd=16792"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "45131069_8_5193-5253",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "5193-5253",
      "markText": "菲利普兄弟公司的天才里奇，当年离职就是因为耶西森的公司收益份额分配不公，缺乏交易自由，而现在里奇却在自己的公司重蹈覆辙。",
      "totalCount": 216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=45131069&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5193&rangeEnd=5253",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c073221072b0a53dc07a5de?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5193&rangeEnd=5253"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "45131069_13_23804-23882",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "23804-23882",
      "markText": "到21世纪头10年中期，在交易商看来，没人想要的大宗商品都可以放到非洲进行处理。它不仅是终极供应商，也是终极买家。由于这些人毫无道德，非洲变成了一个垃圾场。",
      "totalCount": 204,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=45131069&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=23804&rangeEnd=23882",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c073221072b0a53dc07a5de?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=23804&rangeEnd=23882"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "45131069_6_9976-10029",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "9976-10029",
      "markText": "生产一吨铝消耗的电量，相当于一个美国家庭一年的用电量。制铝的能耗相当惊人，因此交易商戏称铝为“凝固的电”。",
      "totalCount": 195,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=45131069&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=9976&rangeEnd=10029",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c073221072b0a53dc07a5de?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=9976&rangeEnd=10029"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "45131069_10_29172-29251",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "29172-29251",
      "markText": "有一点交易商们可能还没有意识到，但是这将很快成为它们通往新财富时代的门票。一个需求自然资源的重要新客户即将出现，这将彻底改变它们的业务——这个新客户就是中国。",
      "totalCount": 192,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=45131069&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=29172&rangeEnd=29251",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c073221072b0a53dc07a5de?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=29172&rangeEnd=29251"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "45131069_3_7250-7319",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "7250-7319",
      "markText": "卡扎菲在西方银行账户存有被冻结的数十亿美元。如果战争结局对维多公司的交易不利，泰勒在西方政府的朋友可以确保使用这些冻结的资产偿还维多公司。",
      "totalCount": 182,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=45131069&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=7250&rangeEnd=7319",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c073221072b0a53dc07a5de?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=7250&rangeEnd=7319"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "45131069_3_2233-2275",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2233-2275",
      "markText": "纵观全球，石油、金钱与权力密不可分。基于此，他从不回避具有更广泛地缘政治意义的交易。",
      "totalCount": 165,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=45131069&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2233&rangeEnd=2275",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c073221072b0a53dc07a5de?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2233&rangeEnd=2275"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "45131069_3_17068-17132",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "17068-17132",
      "markText": "机不可失，交易商随即介入抄底原油，储存起来等待需求恢复。有些交易商甚至以负价格买入，这意味着生产商自己掏腰包让交易商把石油运走。",
      "totalCount": 162,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=45131069&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=17068&rangeEnd=17132",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c073221072b0a53dc07a5de?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=17068&rangeEnd=17132"
    },
